<sect>Introduction
<p>
QMAGICDisplay is a simple event display program for the processed
Monte Carlo events, as given in the output of the programs
<tt>reflector</tt> and <tt>camera</tt>. The supported versions of
these programs are the ones developed by the author of this
application.

